text: Paulding County, Georgia is a county in the U.S. state of Georgia. Its county seat is Dallas. As of 2020, Paulding County had a population of 168,661 people. ==Cities and towns== *Dallas *Hiram *Braswell ==Rural communities== *New Hope *Yorkville *New Georgia *Nebo *Crossroads *Bentwater *Sudie *Seven Hills ==References== Category:1832 establishments in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:Georgia (U.S. state) counties
